@node MAIN "SetSysTime - Contents"

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
                              @{b}@{fg shine}SetSysTime 1.1@{fg text}@{ub}

                 A tool to change and store the systemtime
         for Amiga-systems without a battery backed real-time clock
                       @{fg shine}Copyright © 2006 Peter Riede
                           All Rights Reserved.@{fg text}

                           I hope you like it.
